OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FA church could be forced to close
OL,7,Fafter its treasurer secretly stole
OL,8,Falmost #40,000 from its accounts.
OL,10,FRoger Ward, 61, was the treasurer of
OL,11,Fthe Fourth Church of Christ,
OL,12,FScientist, based on Peter Street in
OL,13,FManchester city centre.
OL,15,FWhile acting as a volunteer trustee,
OL,16,FWard transferred tens of thousands of
OL,17,Fpounds from the church's bank account
OL,18,Finto his own.
