OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FManchester Crown Court heard Ward
OL,7,Fclaimed he moved the money to invest
OL,8,Fin cryptocurrency, hoping to repay the
OL,9,Fchurch and donate extra funds from any
OL,10,Fprofits.
OL,12,FHe said the investment turned out to
OL,13,Fbe a scam and that, in addition to the
OL,14,Fchurch's money, he lost #16,000 of his
OL,15,Fown.
OL,17,FThe court was told there is now a
OL,18,F"real possibility that the church may
OL,19,Fhave to cease all its operations",
OL,20,Fdespite having served the city for
OL,21,Fmore than a century.
