OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FWard had been a trustee since 2017
OL,7,Fand, as treasurer, had sole access to
OL,8,Fthe charity's bank account.
OL,10,FIn July 2024, other trustees became
OL,11,Fconcerned after spotting an
OL,12,Funexplained #1,693 payment to Ward's
OL,13,Fpersonal account. He claimed it was
OL,14,Freimbursement for "legal advice"
OL,15,Flinked to gift aid.
OL,17,FFurther investigation revealed that
OL,18,Fover the following months, Ward
OL,19,Ftransferred around #38,000 into his
OL,20,Fown account. In total, #39,743 was
OL,21,Fstolen, with only #740 repaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
