OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FWard, of Rosgill Drive, Middleton,
OL,7,Fgave "no comment" answers in a police
OL,8,Finterview in November 2024. He later
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to a single charge of
OL,10,Ftheft.
OL,12,FIn a statement, trustee Belinda Hughes
OL,13,Fsaid the loss means there is a "real
OL,14,Fpossibility the church may have to
OL,15,Fcease all its operations".
OL,17,FShe described the church as a "safe
OL,18,Fspace" for members and visitors and
OL,19,Fhighlighted that the building won an
OL,20,Farchitectural award in 1999.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
