OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FThe court heard Ward has two previous
OL,7,Fconvictions for benefit fraud.
OL,9,FHis barrister, Niamh Ingham, asked for
OL,10,Fhim to avoid prison, saying he was the
OL,11,Fsole carer for his adult son and that
OL,12,Fthe family was in "dire" financial
OL,13,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
