OL,3,CChurch treasurer steals nearly #40,000
OL,4,Cfrom charity funds
OL,6,FThe judge, Recorder Jeremy Lasker
OL,7,Frejected the plea and jailed Ward for
OL,8,Ftwo years, telling him: "There is a
OL,9,Freal possibility that the church may
OL,10,Fhave to cease all its operations due
OL,11,Fto the lack of financial resources, as
OL,12,Fa result of your stealing. All this
OL,13,Fhas now been put at risk by virtue of
OL,14,Fyour dishonesty."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
