OL,6,FThe judge added: "You do have, in my
OL,7,Fview, a streak of dishonesty in your
OL,8,Fcharacter. In my judgement, you are
OL,9,Fthe sort of person who is prepared to
OL,10,Fstoop to dishonesty, if you believed
OL,11,Fyou might benefit from it and get away
OL,12,Fwith it."
